('ic4628', '', '', '', 'IC 4628', '', '', '', 'Gum 56', '', 'The Prawn Nebula', 'IC 4628 The Prawn Nebula', 'ic4628.jpg', 'ic4628_thumb.jpg', 'Nebula', 'STL-11000M', 'AT12 IN', 'Paramount ME', 'Selfguide, 10 sec, Bin 2x2', '7 x 20 min Ha Total 2:20', 'Donvale', '2011-07-15', 'IC 4628 also known as  Gum 56 and The Prawn Nebula is about 6,000 light-years away. I took this image under a full moon and it is one of my first images with the AT12IN Scope.', 'ic4628_annotated.jpg', '3 KORRW', '254.254321658964', '-40.342675795898', '1.601751511067', '1.040325119676', '6272.458917338400', '4094.076862287270', '104.540981955640', '68.234614371455', '84.052756955557', 'y'),
