('ngc6559', '', '', 'NGC 6559', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'NGC 6559', 'ngc6559.jpg', 'ngc6559_thumb.jpg', 'Cluster', 'STL-11000M', 'AT8 IN', 'EQ6-Pro', 'Selfguide, 10 sec, Bin 2x2', 'LRGB 40:30:30:30 total 2:10', 'Heathcote', '2012-05-19', 'Located in Sagittarius. Image features the Reflection Nebulae NGC 6559 just above center and IC1274 & IC1275 to the right. Globular cluster NGC 6544 can be seen in the lower left. M8 is just out of view at the bottom.', 'ngc6559_annotated.jpg', 'Paracorr STL', '272.500000000000', '-24.000000000000', '2.010000000000', '1.340000000000', '8064.000000000000', '5364.000000000000', '134.400000000000', '89.400000000000', '0.000000000000', 'y'),
