('rcw038', '', '', '', '', 'RCW 38', '', '', '', '', '', 'RCW 38 : wish upon a star', 'rcw38.jpg', 'rcw38_thumb.jpg', 'Nebula', 'STL-11000M', 'AT8 IN', 'EQ6-Pro', '5 Sec MaximDL', 'LRGBHa 45:45:45:45:70 (4hrs)', 'Heathcote', '2014-03-01', 'RCW 38 is a giant star forming region in Vela. Taken at the ASV Messier Star party. Can you see a face in the image?', 'na', 'Paracorr STL', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'f'),
('rcw040', 'Y', '', '', '', 'RCW 40', '', '', 'GUM 25', '', '', 'RCW 40 / GUM 25', 'rcw40.jpg', 'rcw40_thumb.jpg', 'Nebula', 'STL-11000M', 'AT8 IN', 'EQ6-Pro', '10 Sec Selfguide', 'LRGB 25:25:25:25  (1:40 total)', 'Heathcote', '2014-04-05', 'RCW 40 (also know as GUM 25) is a HII region in Vela. Also in the frame, the small nebula RCW40 to the right and above center. To the left and below center is the small open cluster Markarian 18.', 'na', 'Paracorr STL', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'f'),
('ngc3324b', '', '', 'NGC 3324', 'IC2599', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'NGC 3324 in Carina', 'ngc3324b.jpg', 'ngc3324b_thumb.jpg', 'Nebula', 'STL-11000M', 'AT12 IN', 'Paramount ME', '20Sec Selfguide', 'Ha 8x10mins (1:20 total)', 'Donvale', '2015-01-01', 'Star forming region NGC3324 / IC2599 is an emission nebula located in the constellation Carina. Reflection nebula Gum30 is located at the top left with open cluster NGC 3293. Part of NGC 3372 can be seen at the lower right. Image size: 1.78 x 1.19 deg, Center : 159.275, -58.706', 'ngc3324b_annotated.jpg', '3 KORRW', '159.275000000000', '-58.706000000000', '1.600000000000', '1.020000000000', '6408.000000000000', '4284.000000000000', '106.800000000000', '71.400000000000', '0.000000000000', 'y'),
